{"tid":1533772,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"勇者鬥惡龍馬拉松 - 9月8日撐美大遊行","createTime":"2019-09-02T21:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:49:35.000Z","uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f08a2c26779b1ede56edcb9f2e179610f9e7707","tid":1533772,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:45:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/darkict\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fdarkict&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=df051d52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/darkict</a>"},{"pid":"1a67eab257ea0cbda3ba43f48bab5e96454ae2ae","tid":1533772,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:47:27.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">堅持下去，團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"b09ab9053f1dde490e7